'''''Eminence''''' was the name of two [[Starship/Legends|starships]]:

*'''''[[Eminence (Carrack-class)|Eminence]]''''', an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Carrack-class light cruiser/Legends|''Carrack''-class cruiser]] that participated in the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]]
*'''''[[Eminence (Star Destroyer)|Eminence]]''''', an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] present at the [[Battle of ThonBoka]]

"Eminence" can also refer to:
*a title used by [[Yuuzhan Vong]].
*the [[Eminence (episode)|episode]] in ''[[The Clone Wars: Season Five]]''

